media:group.media:title: What Happened to Golden Sun?
media:group.media:description:
In today's episode of What Happened to....? We explore one of my favorite RPG series of all time, Golden Sun! With only 3 titles to its name, and no presence in over a decade, will we ever see a Golden Sun 4? Let me know in the comments below!
